    "import pysodb\n",
    "sodb = pysodb.SODB()\n",
    "adata_dict = sodb.load_dataset('Dataset9_MS_raw')\n",
    "adata = list(adata_dict.values())[0]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "id": "b4925227-b93b-4f0a-b3bc-04e8b9c4dd15",

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "40119507-3b12-4025-8625-fc29be8cb7ae",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## cell type clustering"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "a9c24c28-5136-4f60-b33f-6d2ae85c4cc8",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "WARNING: adata.X seems to be already log-transformed.\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "sc.pp.filter_genes(adata, min_cells=50)\n",
    "sc.pp.highly_variable_genes(adata, flavor=\"seurat_v3\", n_top_genes=3000)\n",
    "sc.pp.normalize_total(adata, inplace=True)\n",
    "sc.pp.log1p(adata)\n",
    "sc.pp.pca(adata)\n",
    "sc.pp.neighbors(adata)\n",
    "sc.tl.umap(adata)\n",
    "sc.tl.leiden(adata,key_added='ct')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3d071bbe-48cb-4fa7-ad5d-0d71ac6625cd",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## MS"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "193e8a7c-08ce-4f07-9e40-6c242ea01a83",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# initialize the MS object\n",
    "ms = MS.MS(\n",
    "    adata\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# set the number of scales, default is 15\n",
    "ms.set_MS_para(\n",
    "    n_scales=20\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# construct the context-aware representation\n",
    "ms.k_representation_mp()\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "2d0f943c-91ed-40dd-8c46-d464b84c4157",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# identify tissue structure given the number of k\n",
    "ms.run_clustering_normal(\n",
    "    -0.5 \n",
    "    # the clustering parameter\n",
    "    # positive value for the number of clusters\n",
    "    # negative value for the clustering resolution\n",
    ")"
   ]
  },
